	   <tr><td colspan=2>Dwarves and High Elves definantly make the best clerics. But which one is better? I think that depends on your preferance. Dwarves are naturally exellent fighter and High Elves are GREAT casters with high agility (agillity is a VERY important thing, for any class). So, if u want to fight be a dwarf, but of u want to cast be a high elf.<br><br>I personally like High Elves as casters, due to there high agility. It allows you to evade hits easier and u dont take as much damage...so for all casters i suggest High Elves if u can get it. Dwarves as clerics jsut dont work for me...clerics are casters not fighters, they are ment to be in the back buffing and healing and occasionally casting a dd spell.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
